  <h2>Understand Touch-enabled UI and Classic UI</h2> 
  <draft-comment color="yellow" lastModifiedBy="asgupta" lastModifiedDate="2018-07-18T08:24:51.706-0400" prevFirstName="Ashish" prevLastName="Gupta ." type="remark"> 
   <p>Describe RTE UX in different UIs.</p> 
